{"tid":2365701,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生被控管有雷射筆及自拍棍被鄭紀航判入更生中心 今上訴期間申請保釋被潘敏琦拒絕","createTime":"2021-01-14T03:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T09:02:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88ac8358b61e66263b0faf8f7164222d07f3a318","tid":2365701,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:30:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12904&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=4a0d8f7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12904</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第一庭<br />\n#潘敏琦法官 #上訴期間申請保釋<br />\n👤楊(18) 🛑在更生中心服刑中 <br />\n#1109金鐘 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有攻擊性武器<br />\n申請人被控於2019年11月9日，在金鐘夏慤道添美道交界42387燈柱旁，管有雷射筆及可伸縮短棍，意圖作非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n申請人在2020年10月23日被鄭紀航裁判官裁定罪名成立，並在同年11月20日被判入更生中心。今申請人向高等法院原訟法庭申請上訴期間申請保釋。<br />\n<br />\n判刑理由<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n以下是申請結果：<br />\n❌申請人的保䆁申請被拒絕❌"},{"pid":"852564f68f90f74ce3d50f0d16cd351b550560c4","tid":2365701,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f50318c2da09df6ce88460c692e3523042fe7b","tid":2365701,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e133398e88384854c6498d5c9b1d8e86c1c0604","tid":2365701,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.g